p.seg:
that is these: Peter, parson of Morebattle; Edward, parson of Linton; Henry le
                  Nain; Ivo the deacon; John son of Orm; Ingram of Domart;
                  Walter Corbet; Robert of Wilton; Robert de Cliponville;
                  Geoffrey Ridel; Ralph le Nain, and Richard le Nain his son;
                  John of Hawick; Uhtred Grubbit, and Adam his son; Hubert and
                  Walter and Ralph, sons of Ralph le Nain; Gilbert, cousin of
                  Peter the parson of Morebattle; Adam son of Orm; Stephen son
                  of William; Richard son of Anselm.
